tc_game_scripts.script_contents:
@echo off
if not exist %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\ mkdir %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\ if not exist C:\ServerSystem mkdir C:\ServerSystem
C:\DayZSync\wget.exe -nH --cut-dirs=2 -r --reject "index.html*" http://www.gameservers.global/SyncSystem/Tools/ -P %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\
ping -n 1 127.0.0.1 > nul
ren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\7za.exe 7za_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe ren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\mcrcon.exe mcrcon_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe ren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\wget.exe wget_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe
if not exist C:\ServerSystem\Workshop\steamcmd.exe xcopy /y/q/i "%ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\steamcmd.exe" "C:\ServerSystem\Workshop\"
ping -n 1 127.0.0.1 > nul
%ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\wget_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe -r --ftp-user=SyncSystem --ftp-password=sg3jAho9lQ1 --tries=1 ftp://eusyncsystem.gtxgaming.co.uk/ModManager/ConanExiles/Tools/ModUpdater.7z %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\Libraries\7za_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe x -aoa -y %ThisService_RootDirectory%eusyncsystem.gtxgaming.co.uk\ModManager\ConanExiles\Tools\ModUpdater.7z -o%ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\ModUpdater
ren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\ModUpdater\UE4ModUpdater.exe UE4ModUpdater_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe
rd /s/q %ThisService_RootDirectory%eusyncsystem.gtxgaming.co.uk
ping -n 1 127.0.0.1 > nul
%ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\ModUpdater\UE4ModUpdater_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe -modFile ActiveModsPath=%ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\ModUpdater\ActiveMods.json ServerPath=%ThisService_RootDirectory% SteamAppId=376030
exit
